wood films of 1973|1973]] ||''[[Honeymoon (1973 film)|Honeymoon]]'' ||Neelu\n|-\n|[[List of Bollywood films of 1973|1973]] ||''[[Manchali]]'' ||Pushpa\n|-\n|[[List of Bollywood films of 1973|1973]] ||''Alam Ara'' ||\n|-\n|[[List of Bollywood films of 1974|1974]] || ''[[Albeli]]'' ||\n|-\n|[[List of Bollywood films of 1974|1974]] ||''Ujala Hi Ujala''||Gita\n|-\n|[[List of Bollywood films of 1974|1974]] ||''[[Amir Garib]]'' ||Anju\n|-\n|[[List of Bollywood films of 1975|1975]] ||''[[Sanyasi (1975 film)|Sanyasi]]'' ||Aarti\n|-\n|[[List of Bollywood films of 1975|1975]] ||''Dayar-e-Madina'' ||Main lead<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thehindu.com/features/friday-review/blast-from-the-past-dayaremadina-1975/article7404136.ece|title=Dayar-e-Madina (1975)|website=The Hindu|date=9 July 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[List of Bollywood films of 1975|1975]] ||''[[Ranga Khush]]'' ||Devi\n|-\n|[[List of Bollywood films of 1975|1975]] ||''Badnaam'' ||Meena<ref>{{cite web|url=http://muvyz.com/moviepage/ye519824|title=Badnaam 1975|website=Muvyz}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[List of Bollywood films of 1986|1986]] || ''[[Love And God]]'' ||Starting production in 1963 released in 1986\n|}\n\n== Awards and nominations ==\n*1965: [[Bengal Film Journalists Association Awards]] - Best Supporting Actress (Hindi), ''Arzoo'' (1965)\n*1972 - [[Filmfare]] nomination as Best Supporting Actress for ''[[Beimaan]]''\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb name|0623416}}\n* [https://myviewsonbollywood.wordpress.com/2017/11/23/remembering-the-lovely-actress-nazima-who-died-at-the-young-age-of-27/ Remembering the lovely actress NAZIMA who died at the young age of 27!]\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Indian film actresses]]\n[[Category:Place of birth missing (living people)]]\n[[Category:1946 births]]\n", "name_user": "Will Sandberg", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nazima"}
